description:
Go`s Mantyke was spotted near the docks in Kissaki City in the Sinnoh Region. Go`s Scorbunny lured it into the air by kicking a snowball near it and Go captured it.
If competed in an Ice Floe Race in the Sinnoh Region where it allowed Pikachu to ride on its back. They were at the back of the pack as most of the other competitors had already turned past the halfway point when Rocket Gang interfered with the race.
name: Tamanta (Gou)
